summary: An ordinance providing for the rezoning of Lots 3, 4, 5 and 6, Block 33, Denny & Hoyt's Addition, located on the north side of North 34th Street between Fremont Avenue and Aurora Avenue; and Lots 5 and 6, Block 1, Struve's Addition, located on the northeast corner of 12th Avenue and Yesler Way, with respect to Use Districts, and amending Ordinance No. 45382, as amended, by adding thereto one new section to be numbered 2-17.
